  characterSystem:
    characterName: Dick Allford
    hejFras: "Oh? Didn\u2019t see you there."
    hejFrasEvent:
      Guid:
        Data1: -886890451
        Data2: 1151448236
        Data3: 55499665
        Data4: 350021730
      Path: event:/Dick/Dick Hej
    firstQuestion:
      question: "This party is the bees knees! What\u2019s the occasion? "
      answer: "Didn\u2019t you read the invitation? It\u2019s for my beautiful Barbra,
        it\u2019s her birthday! Didn\u2019t you get a present you rube!"
    q1FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: "I didn\u2019t know you had a wife?"
      answer: "Not a wife you knucklehead! Barbra is my darling dog, not my bird!?
        No, I've been single for quite some time\u2026"
    q1FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: "Does that mean you\u2019re fishing\u2026 for a date? "
      answer: "Well\u2026 I\u2026 uh\u2026 I\u2019m pretty shy on dates\u2026 but
        I\u2019m sure Barbra would like the company! "
    secondQuestion:
      question: Why is both a reporter and the constable here?
      answer: "Well.. there\u2019s been some rumors that this ball is a cover up,
        but that's just some bum rap! This party\u2019s purpose is only to let those
        jitterbugs out there knock it out! "
    q2FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: 'Then, may I have this next dance? '
      answer: "No no\u2026 I\u2019m a terrible dancer, always been. Thank you though,
        you gotta have some moxie to ask the host for a dance! "
    q2FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: 'Is bravery something you admire? '
      answer: 'Of course! This world only rewards the courageous, like myself. I
        wouldn''t be this killer diller without it. '
    thirdQuestion:
      question: 'Holy Mackrel Mr Allford, what brand is this champagne? '
      answer: 'Well natch! Franc bluve always makes my parties swell! '
    q3FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: 'Gee, that sounds like it drains the clams! '
      answer: "Could I tell you a secret? It\u2019s not that expensive, but it gives
        you a good buzz! Don\u2019t tell the other guests though, that dandy over
        there seems to have some expensive taste when it comes to booze. "
    q3FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: "That\u2019s some shady tactics! "
      answer: "I have nothing to hide! I just don\u2019t want to reveal all of my
        cards. "
    "hejD\xE5Fras": "Don\u2019t flip your wig out there!"
